nodes.text: Star Wars Storytime Tin is a boxed set of young-readers books. It was published by Disney–Lucasfilm Press on July 20, 2015. The set's contents include the Star Wars Galactic Adventures storybook, the Star Wars Doodles coloring-and-activity book, the Star Wars Super Stickers storybook, a poster, a picture frame, and a code to redeem the Escape from Darth Vader eBook.
